{"tid":143281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"假「霍士新聞」：曾蔭權獄中自殺亡","createTime":"2017-03-04T13:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T05:04:04.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c710652fb19886a84c00aeb21b894406af9444a9","tid":143281,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:27:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170304/large/1488624055_b53f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170304%2Flarge%2F1488624055_b53f.jpg&h=55635eb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n偽冒霍士新聞的網站頭條標題寫明曾蔭權自殺身亡。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n網上驚現前特首曾蔭權自殺身亡的假新聞！網上一個名為「channel fox」的英文網站，今日大字標題寫明「突發！前香港特首曾蔭權自殺(Breaking！former Hong Kong leader Donald Tsang commits suicide)，該報道引述一名不具名的監獄長向「霍士新聞」記者透露，曾蔭權今早被人發現死於牢房內，並且指經懲教署調查顯示他昨晚服毒自殺，相信與不滿被囚禁有關，相關傳聞今日在網上瘋傳。不過《蘋果》細心發現該網站並非真正霍士新聞的網站( <a href=\"http://www.foxnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=15981a00\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com&h=71f27cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.foxnews.com</a> )，內文亦沒有交代如何向官方確認消息來源。<br />\n<br />\n懲教署發言人指，不會就個別犯人個案作出評論，但有消息指，相關報導不屬實，曾蔭權仍在獄中服刑。"},{"pid":"b735ed27243ee1a01b51cc8086d135e467c9f803","tid":143281,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:27:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170304&amp;guid=56385133&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170304%26guid%3D56385133%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=c8c5d5eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170304%26guid%3D56385133%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=6fabfdb4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170304&amp;guid=56385133&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"a492ca725c31237a130956e691a95b59023d7f3c","tid":143281,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5af24b2dde563ae8cb90100a1fe56da6008539","tid":143281,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T13:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975e350d9c22745ef435c369d3247ab6fa2a3d46","tid":143281,"uid":24139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T14:13:52.000Z","msg":"耐人尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71b981f87aa00c0b1f9599a62662b68d44aac3f","tid":143281,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fe99361e963952a15d87c36f3b867d56bb16da","tid":143281,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"整定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}